{"id":425,"parent_id":0,"book_id":8,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":425,"title":"Elihu","subtitle":"","short_title":"Elihu","uri":"/scriptures/bd/elihu","content":[["div",{"id":"t1","uri":"/scriptures/bd/elihu.t1","order":".000.1108"},[".title","Elihu"],["div",{"id":"p1","uri":"/scriptures/bd/elihu.p1","order":".000.1109"},["i","God (is) He."],"(1) Reproves Job’s three friends and reasons with Job (",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/job/32?span=32-37"},"Job 32–37"],"). See",["i",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bd/job-book-of"},"Job, book of"],"."]],["div",{"id":"p2","uri":"/scriptures/bd/elihu.p2","order":".000.1110"},"(2) An ancestor of Samuel (",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/1.1"},"1 Sam. 1:1"],"); called Eliab (",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-chr/6.27"},"1 Chr. 6:27"],") and Eliel (",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-chr/6.34"},"6:34"],")."],["div",{"id":"p3","uri":"/scriptures/bd/elihu.p3","order":".000.1111"},"(3) Others in",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-chr/12.20"},"1 Chr. 12:20"],"and",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-chr/26.7"},"26:7"],"."],["div",{"id":"p4","uri":"/scriptures/bd/elihu.p4","order":".000.1112"},"(4) There was also an Elihu who lived sometime between Abraham and Moses and who is mentioned as a bearer of the Melchizedek Priesthood prior to Moses. Nothing more is known of him today (",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/84.8-9"},"D&C 84:8–9"],")."]]],"refs":null}
